Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:34.43,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you had a true heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:39.84,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k14}{\k30}o{\k25}mo{\k20}t{\k51}te,{\k0} {\k38}na{\k15}i{\k38}te,{\k0} {\k13}hi{\k18}to{\k0} {\k21}yo{\k9}n{\k39}de,{\k0} {\k14}fu{\k33}wa{\k10}n{\k37}de{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:39.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you would care, cry, call for someone and worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:43.48,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k39}na{\k19}n{\k33}de{\k0} {\k17}i{\k33}ta{\k14}i{\k0} {\k49}no{\k0} {\k41}mo{\k14}t{\k31}te{\k14}n{\k57}da{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:43.48,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you holding onto the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:50.23,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k16}{\k24}bo{\k50}ku{\k0} {\k39}ni{\k0} {\k45}so{\k18}t{\k46}to{\k0} {\k39}a{\k9}zu{\k49}ke{\k50}te{\k0} {\k290}yo{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:50.23,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Share some of it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:55.78,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k16}{\k35}su{\k45}gu{\k0} {\k25}ja{\k0} {\k30}mu{\k48}ri{\k0} {\k19}to{\k0} {\k29}o{\k30}mo{\k17}u{\k0} {\k25}no{\k0} {\k25}na{\k52}ra{\k55}ba{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:55.78,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't think it's possible right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.18,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k9}{\k24}su{\k25}ko{\k29}shi{\k0} {\k49}zu{\k26}tsu{\k0} {\k30}de{\k0} {\k20}i{\k128}i{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.18,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you can do it slowly, bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.28,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k48}tsu{\k12}ba{\k35}sa{\k0} {\k24}no{\k0} {\k29}na{\k19}i{\k0} {\k28}bo{\k22}ku{\k48}ra{\k0} {\k39}ki{\k13}t{\k45}to{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:03.28,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:07.08,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k31}to{\k23}be{\k33}na{\k16}i{\k0} {\k23}to{\k24}ki{\k0} {\k16}mi{\k31}tsu{\k23}ke{\k54}te{\k26}ru{\k0} {\k25}da{\k55}ke{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:07.08,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I'm sure we're only finding times that we can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:11.58,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k15}{\k28}ko{\k48}e{\k0} {\k24}no{\k0} {\k22}ka{\k55}gi{\k21}ri{\k0} {\k30}ki{\k44}mi{\k0} {\k24}wo{\k0} {\k29}yo{\k43}bu{\k0} {\k67}yo{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:11.58,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll call for you to the limits of my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.05,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k9}{\k24}ma{\k26}yo{\k26}wa{\k23}na{\k18}i{\k0} {\k30}yo{\k28}u{\k0} {\k163}ni{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.05,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so that you won't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k28}fu{\k28}wa{\k20}ri{\k0} {\k24}ko{\k50}ko{\k28}ro{\k0} {\k21}ma{\k50}i{\k23}a{\k28}ga{\k25}re{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Soar up to the sky with your gentle heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k17}{\k28}a{\k21}no{\k0} {\k45}ka{\k38}ze{\k0} {\k20}ni{\k0} {\k26}no{\k46}se{\k95}te{\k0} {\k13}i{\k5}s{\k27}se{\k7}i{\k0} {\k10}e{\k26}ro{\k372}se{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ride on that wind, and get it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:35.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The human hat is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all white and pretty, like snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come home with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:51.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:02:00.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't be crying when I'm going to become a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I have to live on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now, Touko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:18.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:20.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:27.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the hot spring reserve on your study trip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:29.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:35.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry for having you pay for the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have a small favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pottery in the mountains near the hot springs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so could you pick up some tea cups for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a call saying that they were almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Shigeru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird laugh, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, when did you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:17.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it natural for your bodyguard to follow you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you so happy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:30.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good to be asked to do a favor for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Great people will eventually meet their ruin,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:50.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,much like dust before the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:53.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's end the morning class here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have free time until lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go to the hot spring first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:04.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have some business to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:21.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sure it's in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you weak little fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hanging around the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore, you useless brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the forest, you useless brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:12.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing bullying this little child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:15.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a human child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:19.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare a human child look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:24.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How impetuous! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:01.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real busybody as always, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, what a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:15.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, the tea cups won't be finished baking until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:19.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are such troublesome creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They go so far just for a container for food,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,yet they could just buy it at the local super market.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being brutally frank saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A body isn't a container, though. {mi mo futa mo nai - saying to mean brutally frank, "no container and no lid". literally, mi can mean body}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, it's going your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:10.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It bounced off you and hit me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:12.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what dinner will be, right, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume laughs often,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems kind of fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,His words, his gestures, his aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,they all seem kind of fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's not really a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:49.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's like me and is disguised as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's lonely like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:57.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He should live in the forest with me, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:16.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm going back tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd feel bad if it got attached to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:06.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go get the tea cups now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows if we can even make it back to class now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm useful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "Thank you" to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not useless anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go gather mushrooms tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather a lot and share some with Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:19.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're still here, you little fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you to get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:36.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any useless brats in this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:37.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not useless anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:58.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The one from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Were my fists not enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:12.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:17.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten, Natsume Reiko-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:23.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you would come and return my name in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:26.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Reiko, she's as cruel as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring? How many springs have passed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, take care of the tea cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, Sawarabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Natsume?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner of the Book of Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for returning it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When they have their names written in it, it serves as a contract and they are then bound to the owner. {check for 3 liner after styling}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll take our names!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:24.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd take your names when he just returned one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me your follower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll be useful to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I won't be useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want us to be bound like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't master and follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we have a different relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:18.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a wonderful color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:23.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The townsfolk introduced me to a good pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Our family has grown, so I thought this was a good chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours, Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that little fox said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,About what, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about whether you're useful or useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show it to Natsume too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be crying when I'm going to become a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:18.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already decided to become strong and to be helpful to Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see Natsume that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:34.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You met the owner of the Book of Friends, Natsume, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't disguise yourself as a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:49.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can fill me up with fish, then I'll tell you a way to see Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me how to see Natsume now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:21.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a foolish little fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You were tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:27.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always alone because you're so stupid. {stupid doesn't seem like the right word here but ok}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume already forgot about you a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, little fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's medicine that will allow you to become a human for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine to become a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to see him, you can go see him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I just have to go see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:27.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm a fox too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:30.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I go to the world of humans, I can follow Natsume's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:56.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Natsume is feeling lonely being by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume's scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natsume's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:48.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you okay by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull it in! Pull it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You again, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:21.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught a whole bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natsume's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all fried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the landlocked masu salmon Natsume caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, what a fine salmon you caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat, Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours has the skin, Takashi, so is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like anything, tell me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigure-san doesn't like green peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:28.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, when I was young, I didn't like them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so I've got a friend here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:41.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this salmon is pretty good, Touko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll have some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:48.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:07.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Natsume looked like he was having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the lonely one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,it was the little fox from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a cute hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go have dinner and then I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to remember the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was lonely, I was afraid of going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even think of doing something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:54.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably didn't notice many things.
